w stated it was in the shade until the afternoon, I found it to be in the sun the whole day and got a great tan!There are several restaurants in the hotel which cater for all tastes; we mainly ate at the market café which offered dozens of different dishes in a buffet style. I celebrated my birthday whilst on holiday there and returned to the room that night to find the most delicious chocolate cake with a Happy Birthday note from the hotel staff. I have stayed in many ‘grand’ hotels before but none have ever made my stay so personal. I found the service from the staff (in ALL areas) absolutely fantastic. Their attitude and commitment to service were second to none and I wouldn’t hesitate to recommend this hotel to anyone.	
